{
  "stem": "942.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it took them quite a while, until they got a thread of a lead, you know, where we were taken.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they sort of followed all the way up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they came up to-- to this place in [NON-ENGLISH], a couple of days after we have left for home, you see?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So then, they started to follow the train back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got off the train, so they missed us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They caught up to the train at another station, and we were not on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So anyway, we got home before they did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember coming back to my little town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this was-- it was in July, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had a lot of big story to tell all my friends, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I remember, my grandmother, she cooked up a big-- she made a chicken, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I just remember the smell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the cucumber salad, it's still with me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, all of us kids, we went to the river, you know, to swim and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was a real big hero.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I could tell a big story, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "None of us kids have traveled on such a long journey ever before, you know, in this little town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So my father came home-- and my uncle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I just can't remember how they settled this situation for them deserting, you know, the labor camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But I think it was settled in some way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So this was 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And by this time, I was out of school, you know, because there was no point in me going to school.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the Hebrew school was finished, because the teacher was taken away to forced labor camp as well.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
